  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A survey of health beliefs and cancer screening behaviour and intentions in Hodgkin lymphoma&#xD;
      survivors&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A survey of Hodgkin lymphoma survivors registered in a follow-up database, examining health&#xD;
      beliefs (using Health Belief Model) around breast, bowel and lung cancer screening, previous&#xD;
      screening uptake and future uptake intentions&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
